sentences: Takayuki Haga (芳賀 隆之, Haga Takayuki, born January 26, 1955), better known by the stage name George Tokoro (所ジョージ, Tokoro Jōji), is a Japanese comedian, TV personality, singer-songwriter, and essayist.
